    • Method Detail

      • init

        public static SW_ResourceCorePackage init()
        Creates, registers, and initializes the Package for this model, and for any others upon which it depends.

        This method is used to initialize SW_ResourceCorePackage.eINSTANCE when that field is accessed. Clients should not invoke it directly. Instead, they should simply access that field to obtain the package.

        See Also:
        SW_ResourceCorePackage.eNS_URI, createPackageContents(), initializePackageContents()
